{"tid":2305091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星月居、泉章居及8½ Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA共十多人感染，本月中後到訪者需強制檢測","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T14:09:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1bafc30c7a02440d49503a5207f8f1905e9ea9b5","tid":2305091,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562640-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562640-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGibY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=5c1675e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562640-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=04447f47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562640-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增115宗新型肺炎確診個案，其中62宗屬歌舞群組，歌舞群組目前累計479宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n新增個案中有24宗源頭不明，23宗與其他群組相關。另外有50多宗初步確診個案，有餐廳、院舍及學校出現感染。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，有3間食肆的員工及食客受感染，3間食肆分別為灣仔莊士企業大廈的「星月居」、中環歷山大廈的「8&frac12; Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA」，以及上環誠信大廈的「泉章居」。中心指，政府稍後會發公告，強制要求本月15日或之後曾到訪有關食肆的市民接受病毒檢測。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，3間食肆目前合共有十多人感染，包括侍應、樓面、廚師、清潔及食客。"},{"pid":"56bcf6ab5e4ca48684389e4929d8b866c365ff21","tid":2305091,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"how do they know who been there?"},{"pid":"18b29a4c4c611f0d23a6067d5751a621a50b7522","tid":2305091,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56bcf6ab5e4ca48684389e4929d8b866c365ff21","tid":2305091,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"how do they know who been there?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"credit card / 八達通"},{"pid":"28e7fe1ee70318ff0b7bd14215174d53bb0a187c","tid":2305091,"uid":23303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56bcf6ab5e4ca48684389e4929d8b866c365ff21","tid":2305091,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"how do they know who been there?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"睇返booking list 咪得"},{"pid":"bc0aeedd6aefb26281884acb5085e477e44f8563","tid":2305091,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"如果啲食客冇睇到呢單新聞點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係有專人通知佢哋"},{"pid":"e24a1ac7b60f8b4dacd0484eab0d72d58966863e","tid":2305091,"uid":247896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"希望快啲出現第一個冇去強制檢測但後來俾人捉到兼重罰嘅人，咁先收到阻嚇作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a26f0df62d7bae414fd448dab10ab57d1cb7a5","tid":2305091,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56bcf6ab5e4ca48684389e4929d8b866c365ff21","tid":2305091,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"how do they know who been there?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"未必知<br />\n不過事後被發現就會告多條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1abe8e6cb7ba6707d3fdef578f5446f359449f6","tid":2305091,"uid":77677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"應該有好多所謂網紅 有錢人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}